  "42 - Purge du circuit secondaire du bloc ABS": {
   "width": 13260,
   "height": 9540,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Purge du circuit secondaire du bloc ABS/ESP",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1920,
      "top": 240,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 9240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Pour r\u00e9aliser la purge du circuit secondaire du bloc hydraulique et afin de ne pas introduire d'air,  il faut:",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-1- s'assurer que le circuit de freinage du v\u00e9hicule a \u00e9t\u00e9 purg\u00e9 par la m\u00e9thode de purge traditionnelle.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-2- moteur coup\u00e9, apr\u00e8s 3 appuis sur la p\u00e9dale de frein, contr\u00f4ler la course de la p\u00e9dale qui doit \u00eatre correcte (p\u00e9dale dure).",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 1800,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-3- installer l'appareil de purge sur le bocal de liquide frein.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 2400,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-4- s'assurer que les vis de purge (purgeur) soient ferm\u00e9es.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 2760,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-5- appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant le pression sur celle ci lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue ARG.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 3120,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-6- attendre la fin du cycle avant de relacher la p\u00e9dale.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 3720,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-7- purger la roue ARG afin d\u00e9vacuer l'air dans ce circuit, puis refermer le purgeur",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 4080,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
